sted-after-climbing-new-yorks-empire-state-building-to-propose/articleshow/132140394.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-02T20:24:41+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132141167,imgsize-134550.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Tax cuts, pension overhaul and sick leave reforms: Germany launches sweeping economic overhaul]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132140980.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Under Chancellor Friedrich Merz, the government has rolled out a transformative economic reform initiative intended to enhance Germany's financial landscape. The plan encompasses significant tax cuts for families, adjustments in the pension system that raise the retirement age, and new sick leave policies that require doctor’s notes from day one.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/tax-cuts-pension-overhaul-and-sick-leave-reforms-germany-launches-sweeping-economic-overhaul/articleshow/132140980.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/tax-cuts-pension-overhaul-and-sick-leave-reforms-germany-launches-sweeping-economic-overhaul/articleshow/132140980.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-02T20:10:43+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Business Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132140980,imgsize-212358.cms"/></item></channel></rss>